refsect1.para:
The class &class_smt_lib_solver; is a base class for SMT solvers that read the SMT-LIB format [Silvio Ranise and Cesare Tinelli. The SMT-LIB
Standard: Version 1.1. Technical Report, Department of Computer Science, The University of Iowa, 2005. (Available at
)]. It inherits from the class &class_smt_solver;.
